graph TD
    Auth([1. Auth - Google OAuth optional])
    Ideation[2. Ideation - Enter theme brainstorm concepts select one]
    PromptBuild[3. Prompt Building - Load or build prompts generate N low-res images]
    Variants[4. Variant Generation - Review variants optional BG removal rerender or approve]
    Finalize[5. Finalization - Upscale selected variant to chosen resolution optional BG removal]
    Publish[6. Publish - Configure Printify product upload optional publish to store]

    Auth --> Ideation
    Ideation --> PromptBuild
    PromptBuild --> Variants
    Variants --> Finalize
    Finalize --> Publish

